data.description: Must see 4 bed/2 bath home in a high demand Central Valley neighborhood! Pergo floors, open kitchen, and lots of natural light are just some of the draws to this wonderful home.  Beautiful fenced back yard with a covered deck, bar-b-que area, in-ground pool (with it's own perimeter fence), and a large grass area. Large family room with a gas fireplace. Also features gas forced air heat with central A/C, gas hot water heater, sprinkler system, covered front porch and a 2 car garage with opener. You'll be happy you came to see this one!
